snippet: The Liberty tied the franchise season record for wins by beating the Lynx for their 22nd victory and moved one and a half games ahead of Minnesota in the race for home-court advantage throughout the postseason.
abstract: New York Liberty beat Minnesota Lynx, 75-71, to grab top seed in WNBA Eastern Conference.
lead_paragraph: The Liberty tied the franchise season record for wins by beating the Lynx for their 22nd victory and moved one and a half games ahead of Minnesota in the race for home-court advantage throughout the postseason.

headline.print_headline: Liberty Secure Top Seed in the East
headline.main: Liberty Secure Top Seed in the East
